data.description: Charming home located on one of Upper Arlingtons most beautiful streets. Perfect for someone wanting to add their personal touches and make their own. Over 2400 square feet of existing home with with an impressive 66 by 240 foot lot on which to expand. Beautiful wood floors through out this 3 bedroom including a unique in law suite on first floor. Conveniently the three full bathrooms are located within each bedroom in addition to the one half bath downstairs for guests. Home also  boasts a large three car detached garage.  Fabulous location within the Upper Arlington school district, This home is a must see.
